data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
1. Once the Hyperterm terminal is open, type “M” to begin the memory test.
2. The board should report “NONE!” for total errors. If any RAM errors are indicated, the board must be rejected
3.Type “S” to begin the "Flash Scan" test.
4. If the tester reports either of the first two blocks (0-1), or any of the last 6 blocks (4090-4095) as bad,call Test engineer
5. Close Hyperterminal sofware.
